Class NBTHandler<T extends de.tr7zw.changeme.nbtapi.NBTCompound>

java.lang.Object
de.dei0.blockprot.bukkit.nbt.NBTHandler<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the NBT container. NBTCompound is the base of all containers and works with all of them, however there are some special conditions and functions for specific containers.
Direct Known Subclasses:
BukkitStatistic, FriendHandler, FriendSupportingHandler, RedstoneSettingsHandler, StatHandler
public abstract class NBTHandler<T extends de.tr7zw.changeme.nbtapi.NBTCompound> extends Object
The base NBT Handler.

0.3.0
